overview: At the beginning of 209, the Lord spoke a prophetic word to Pastor Kilpatrick. In mere seconds, a download of revelation and prophecy came. The Lord gave the word R.E.S.U.R.R.E.C.T.I.O.N. to highlight twelve insights concerning the future.
tagline: A Prophetic Insight for the Future
title: R.E.S.U.R.R.E.C.T.I.O.N.
